# Sovereign Identity Engine

## Decentralized Identity Infrastructure for Web3

Sovereign Identity Engine is an open-source identity verification layer built for Web3 applications.

It enables:
- 🔐 Verifiable Credentials
- ✍️ ECDSA Signature Verification
- 🧬 Decentralized Identity Profiles
- 📊 Reputation & Identity Scoring
- 🔗 Blockchain Identity Intelligence
- 🌐 Base Network Integration

## Core Vision

Build a trusted identity layer where users, applications, and organizations can verify digital identity without centralized control.

## Technology Stack

Ethereum • Base Network • DID • Verifiable Credentials • Cryptographic Proofs

## Current Release

V13.1.0  
Production Prototype

## Security

✓ Private keys excluded  
✓ Cryptographic proof manifests  
✓ Signature validation  
✓ Issuer verification  

## Demo

Live identity verification flow:
Identity → Credential → Signature → Verification

## Mission

Create an open identity protocol for the next generation of Web3 applications.
